name: Crowbar Climber
summary:
🌟Mega Update Packed with a New Challenge! 🌟
Welcome to Crowbar Heaven: a brand-new stage where fallen Crowbar Climbers gather and mischievous angels get in your way!
This time, we’re releasing not one but TWO stages! A paid stage and a free stage!

Climb your way to the top and you’ll earn yourself a special skin just for making it!
Are you ready to take on this new challenge?

This game is a challenge for all VR gamers who love physics and brain teasers.
